For zero-alloc on .NET 6+, use `stackalloc` + `TryFormat`:
```csharp
Span<char> buffer = stackalloc char[32];
value.TryFormat(buffer, out int written, format, formatProvider);
// concat with symbol into final string
return string.Concat(buffer[..written], " ", symbol);
